# The gomobile-built native binding is a build artifact — build it locally
# (see README.md). Everything else in app/libs/ (the .gitkeep) is tracked.
# gomobile bind emits both the .aar and a -sources.jar beside it.
app/libs/*.aar
app/libs/*.jar
